thread.title: BRIEF-Telemedycyna Polska Raises Its Share Capital By Series C Shares Issue

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Telemedycyna Polska Raises Its Share Capital By Series C Shares Issue
text:
Feb 15 (Reuters) - TELEMEDYCYNA POLSKA SA:
* RESOLVES TO RAISE ITS SHARE CAPITAL BY 88,165 ZLOTYS TO 668,165 ZLOTYS
* UPS SHARE CAPITAL VIA ISSUE OF 881,646 NEW SERIES C SHARES AT ISSUE PRICE OF 1.60 ZLOTY PER SHARE
* TOTAL VALUE OF SERIES C SHARES ISSUE AMOUNTS TO 1.4 MILLION ZLOTYS
* SERIES C SHARES OFFERED IN PRIVATE SUBSCRIPTION WITHOUT PRE-EMPTIVE RIGHTS Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
